data.description: Beautifully remodeled 2 story, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom PUD, nice kitchen and bathrooms. new laminated floors and a pantry room. Laundry area, and a separate 2 car garage. Pleasant backyard for entertainment.  Great for an FHA loan. This complex is like living in paradise, with a nice swimming pool and a club house across the street. Property is located within  a very short walking distance to Cambridge elementary school.  This is a must see.
